    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes how the Alternate-Marking Method can be used as a passive performance measurement tool in an IPv6 domain.  It defines an Extension Header Option to encode Alternate-Marking information in both the Hop-by-Hop Options Header and Destination Options Header.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
